args.code:
import PyPDF2

with open('./31-Syn-Chain/Syn-Chain-ABSA/paper.pdf', 'rb') as f:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)
    num_pages = len(reader.pages)
    text = ''
    for i in range(min(num_pages, 5)):
        text += reader.pages[i].extract_text() + '\n---PAGE BREAK---\n'

print(text[:2000])
